(1) Host
---------
==> sets or returns the hostname and port of a URL
==> If the port number is not specified in the URL (or if it is the scheme's default port - like 80, or 443), some browsers will not display the port number.


EX: Get Host Name Of [http://www.example.com/test.htm#part2]
-----

	window.location.host // "www.example.com"
	
	Or 
	
	location.host // "www.example.com"
	
	
EX: Set Host Name Of [http://www.example.com/test.htm#part2]
-----

	window.location.host = "www.google.com"
	
	Or
	
	location.host = "www.google.com"
	
	Or 
	
	location.host = "localhost:3000"
